rtTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531437\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531437\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 11, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104quu1665702559831.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quu1665702559831.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quu1665702559831.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"quu1665702559831\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $item\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"quu1665702559831___item_270993\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the value that corresponds to a given ID in an associative list.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"quu1665702559831__topic_d85016e1_d85017e1_d85018e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702559831__p_d85019e1_d85020e1_d85021e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$item</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ID</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">AssociativeList</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702559831__topic_d56402e1_d56403e1_d56404e1_d56405e1_d56406e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d137336e82\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quu1665702559831__li_d34595e1_d34596e1_d34597e1\">Value that corresponds to the given ID in an associative list.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quu1665702559831__li_d34598e1_d34599e1_d34600e1\">NULL (\"\"), if <var class=\"keyword varname\">ID</var> is not found in <var class=\"keyword varname\">AssociativeList</var>; <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> is set to UPROCERR_ITEM (-1129).\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702559831__topic_d56407e1_d56408e1_d56409e1_d56410e1_d56411e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d137336e106\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702559831__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702559831__topic_d56412e1_d56413e1_d56414e1_d56415e1_d56416e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d137336e115\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702559831__p_d85034e1_d85035e1_d85036e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$item</span> function acts in the same way as the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getitem/id</span> ProcScript statement, but can also be used as part of an expression.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702559831__p_d85037e1_d85038e1_d85039e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ayl1665702554178.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ayl1665702554178.html\" title=\"A list is a group of related items homogeneous items collected into a single unit, the list. Every item in a list is assumed to have the same structure.\">Lists and Sublists</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702559831__section_akz_gw1_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d137336e141\">Example: Find and Pass Associative List Items</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to find and directly pass an\n               associative list item to a ProcScript module:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"quu1665702559831__pre_csj_hw1_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($item(\"MEDIUM\", myList) = \"Book\")\n call selectBook($item(\"ISBN_NR\", myList))\nendif</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cip1665702554022.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>List Handling in ProcScript</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript instructions that enable you to build lists, retrieve items from lists, and sort lists based on various criteria.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gan1665702559756.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$idpart</a><p>Return the ID part of an associative list item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ytj1665702559912.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$valuepart</a><p>Return the value part of an associative list item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzk1665702559988.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$itemnr</a><p>Return the list item that corresponds to a given index number in a list.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531437\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531437\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$item Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 11, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $item Return the value that corresponds to a given ID in an associative list. $item ( ID , AssociativeList ) Return Values Value that corresponds to the given ID in an associative list. NULL (\"\"), if ID is not found in AssociativeList ; $procerror is set to UPROCERR_ITEM (-1129). Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $item function acts in the same way as the getitem/id ProcScript statement, but can also be used as part of an expression. For more information, see Lists and Sublists . Example: Find and Pass Associative List Items The following example shows how to find and directly pass an associative list item to a ProcScript module: if ($item(\"MEDIUM\", myList) = \"Book\") call selectBook($item(\"ISBN_NR\", myList)) endif Copy Related Links List Handling in ProcScript Uniface provides ProcScript instructions that enable you to build lists, retrieve items from lists, and sort lists based on various criteria. $idpart Return the ID part of an associative list item. $valuepart Return the value part of an associative list item. $itemnr Return the list item that corresponds to a given index number in a list. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}